Debian/ubuntu
apt-get update
apt-get install transmission-daemon -y
/etc/init.d/transmission-daemon stop
nano /var/lib/transmission-daemon/info/settings.json
需要修改的如下：(记得开端口和51413)
"rpc-password"			# 访问密码
"rpc-username"			# 登录用户名
"rpc-whitelist": "*"	# 通过ip访问则需要允许所有ip访问
"rpc-port"				# 访问端口
启动/etc/init.d/transmission-daemon start
服务式命令service transmission-daemon start/stop
卸载sudo apt-get autoremove --purge transmission-daemon
